headline: Garmin announces new Montana handheld GPS series with optional SOS satellite communication capabilities to help you stay in touch
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) today announced a new Montana® series – the Montana 710, Montana 710i and robust Montana 760i – to its collection of handheld GPS navigators. All three handhelds feature durable, easy-to-view, 5-inch color touchscreen displays that are glove-friendly. These versatile devices are ideal for use during a variety of outdoor activities, including hiking, mountain biking, off-road riding and more.
